DOC.brief_summary: This study is designed to compare the effectiveness and ease of use of two commonly used NCPAP interfaces: the RAM NC and the Infant Flow prongs and nasal mask.
DOC.brief_title: Comparison of RAM Cannula Nasal Continuous Positive Airway Pressure Versus Infant Flow Nasal Continuous Positive Airway Pressure (NCPAP)
DOC.criteria: less than or equal to 7 kg order for nasal continuous positive pressure patients greater than 7kg patients that do not have informed consent
